Greeneview Athletics
February 22, 2019 at 12:41 PM ·

College Signing

Congratulations to the Tamplin Family - Ian will be attending and playing football for Division 3 National Power Mount Union.

District Bowling Tournament

Anna Willingham competed as an individual in the District Tourney and had a high game of 180, her total series was 494 for the 3 games. It took a 562 to qualify for State this year.

The Boys team finished in 14th place out of 16 teams with a score of 3549. Kenton Ridge won the District with 4158 with Mechanicsburg 2nd, and Versailles 3rd joining them qualifying to State. Braedan Brennaman had the high game for the Rams with a 219. Braedan had a 581 series and it took 643 to qualify to State.

Tonight Feb 22

High School Boys Basketball Tournament at Northmont 6:00pm vs Twin Valley South. Tickets on sale at High School until 2:30. Contact Mr Rinehart for special arrangements for ticket purchases.

High School Wrestling Sectionals at Lehman Catholic 5:00pm. Wrestling will continue on Saturday starting at 10:00am.

Good Luck Rams !
